EXPRESSION: CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(ESN_TRANS_OTHER_BANK_1_0.TRANS_DATE),'') = '' THEN to_date('1000-01-03') ELSE (COALESCE(to_date(ESN_TRANS_OTHER_BANK_1_0.TRANS_DATE , 'yyyy-MM-dd'), to_date('1000-01-03'))) END

(CAST (CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(ESN_TRANS_OTHER_BANK_1_0.TRANS_TIME),'') = '' THEN '00:00:00' ELSE  (SUBSTR(ESN_TRANS_OTHER_BANK_1_0.TRANS_TIME,1,2))|| ':' ||  (SUBSTR(ESN_TRANS_OTHER_BANK_1_0.TRANS_TIME,4,2)) || ':' ||  (SUBSTR(ESN_TRANS_OTHER_BANK_1_0.TRANS_TIME,7,2)) END AS VARCHAR(8)))
LEFT(CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(replace(DEBIT_DATE, '-', '')),'') = '' THEN CAST('10000103' AS VARCHAR(8)) ELSE replace(DEBIT_DATE, '-', '') END,8)
LEFT(CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(replace(SEND_DATE, '-', '')),'') = '' THEN CAST('10000103' AS VARCHAR(8)) ELSE replace(SEND_DATE, '-', '') END,8)

CASE WHEN COALESCE(TRIM(ESN_TRANS_OTHER_BANK_1_0.CREDIT_DATE),'') = '' THEN to_date('1000-01-03') ELSE (COALESCE(to_date(ESN_TRANS_OTHER_BANK_1_0.CREDIT_DATE , 'yyyy-MM-dd'), to_date('1000-01-03'))) END
